{"tid":115724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[讀書會]入黎講下最近睇完/睇緊咩書","createTime":"2017-02-10T18:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T00:32:34.000Z","uid":34677,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65b8e0da823e1fc1624b95adbe9781cd2aa1ce46","tid":115724,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"分享下最近睇完/睇緊咩書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係講下黎近想睇咩書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇完一本法農(Frantz Fanon)既書<br />\n黑皮膚●白面具 (Black Skin, white mask)<br />\n我覺得係幾好睇既 <br />\n後半部分有關精神病學既比較難明<br />\n當中描述當年既黑人被殖民其實好值得香港人相家去反思我地如何被西方世界影響<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家睇緊咩書呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62595d6e3ba74b100302523d022a02bc51583874","tid":115724,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:30:27.000Z","msg":"鬼吹燈，會唔會對樓主黎講好俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab8eee11267ed50de725e7df711f2666faf8138","tid":115724,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:31:24.000Z","msg":"1Q84 第一冊睇左大半覺得好悶好難頂，好無放棄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5ac7dc91044c59477efc8ef9a1d2b166a01e68","tid":115724,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼吹燈，會唔會對樓主黎講好俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩書都得 因為一黎想帶起呢度有讀書會<br />\n二黎覺得香港讀書風氣唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩書都可以聽下"},{"pid":"9541b5de2ad0c8ce050284196948936e1e0620d0","tid":115724,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鬼吹燈，會唔會對樓主黎講好俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />